&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Unit of an idea is a thought  &lt;br&gt;
A thought of love, respect, value, care, preservation, etc.  &lt;br&gt;
Let’s call this X thought.  &lt;br&gt;
Or thought of disrespect, discouragement, carelessness, demolition, etc.  &lt;br&gt;
Let’s call this Y thought.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Based on our understanding of life,  &lt;br&gt;
the environment around and our value system,  &lt;br&gt;
We may choose to apply X thought  &lt;br&gt;
or Y thought on the concepts of  &lt;br&gt;
nation, a particular religion, caste of people, color of people,  &lt;br&gt;
geography of people, nationality of people,  &lt;br&gt;
praying method of people, and the belief system of the people.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
